    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Your eyes bulge from their sockets and extend upwards from your head on long, prehensile stalks, greatly enhancing your eyesight and field of view but leaving you unable to close your eyes, increasing your vulnerability to harmful visual effects.  \n   \n **Benefit** You gain all-around vision, a +2 item bonus to visual Perception checks, and low-light vision if you don\u2019t already have it. These effects last for 1 minute.  \n   \n **Drawback** For 1 minute, you take a \u20132 penalty to saving throws against effects that have the visual trait.",
        "level": 7,
        "traits": [
            {
